 这三者同时存在时容易发生互相覆盖的情况：
 
 /* 附带（从左往右）渐变色（兼容写法） */
    background: url("../images/turn01.png") no-repeat 72% 5px,url("../images/turn02.png") no-repeat 35% 5px,-webkit-linear-gradient(left, #082250, #083fa1,#082250); /* Safari 5.1 - 6.0 */
    background: url("../images/turn01.png") no-repeat 72% 5px,url("../images/turn02.png") no-repeat 35% 5px,-o-linear-gradient(right, #082250, #083fa1,#082250); /* Opera 11.1 - 12.0 */
    background: url("../images/turn01.png") no-repeat 72% 5px,url("../images/turn02.png") no-repeat 35% 5px,-moz-linear-gradient(right, #082250, #083fa1,#082250); /* Firefox 3.6 - 15 */
    background: url("../images/turn01.png") no-repeat 72% 5px,url("../images/turn02.png") no-repeat 35% 5px,linear-gradient(to right, #082250, #083fa1,#082250); /* 标准的语法 */
